metadata.name: colorful okinawa
metadata.description:
There are many beautiful sights in Okinawa that I see.

The pink glowing flower is bougainvillea.
The language of flowers is "passion" and "I only see you.

The flower shining in golden color is Blumeria.
The language of flowers is "Wishing happiness for your loved ones.

The crystal clear sea and the lush nature are vivid and unforgettably beautiful once seen.

As you grow older, you will see more and more of Okinawa's charms that you did not understand when you were a child.

The blue ribbon pattern worn by the girl is a mincer pattern that has been handed down from Okinawa's ancient history, and it represents the wish of the people of Okinawa for "long-lasting happiness throughout the ages.

Shy and peace-loving Okinawans rarely say "I love you" in words, but they convey their romantic feelings through their culture and costumes.

I would be happy if many people could understand the charm of Okinawa, which cannot be conveyed in words alone: nature, culture, and people.
